&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Good Pill is reimagining what a pharmacy can be for families across Georgia. By pairing transparent, affordable pricing with surplus medicine that would otherwise be wasted, we help people get the prescriptions they need without the financial stress, and we’re improving health for millions in the process.&lt;/p&gt;
